author: Paul V
title: Re: ‘No one is this dumb’: Sarah Silverman confuses surveyor’s mark with a swastika?
text:
Maybe she doesn’t have Google: Do you not have Google? https://t.co/TYGShXrwFh 
— Jim Antle (@jimantle) February 13, 2017 The premise on its face is incredibly dumb. Then you realize she indignantly asked if they have Google while failing to use Google herself. https://t.co/Xl6e7rTuQH 
— Eric Spencer (@JustEric) February 13, 2017 
Now we do realize she might be joking. But if she is, we agree with this: If this is supposed to be satire, it explains why @SarahKSilverman just isn't funny to most people. https://t.co/6Aaf6voc9Q 
— Drunken Uncle (@DrunkenUncle_) February 13, 2017 
***
